name: Stripey Thigh-High Socks LoRA
description:
Everybody loves striped thigh high socks, right? Unfortunately, I found a great number of the excellent checkpoints on this site have a devil of a time rendering actual stripes on stockings. So, I made this LoRA to try and fix that. This is just the version 1 of this. I am sure I will come back later, do another version and maybe even combine versions 1 and 2 for a super-LoRA!

Trigger word is stripedsocks. I recommend using "[color1] striped socks" where color1 is whatever color you want. Usually, with that prompt, the models will do Color + White stripes. If you do "[Color 1] and [Color 2] striped socks", that works about 80% of the time. If you go with three or more colors, though, the patterning goes all weird and you get what you get.

I have tested with several different models and it worked well with each. Recommend a strength of 0.75-1.
